  "detailed_description": "IMPULSE is a no-frills, high-speed, purely-competitive game of carball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNo glitch exploitation.<br />\r\nNo nonsense.<br />\r\nPure carball.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHate competitive matches? Don’t play this game.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll cars are equal:<br />\r\n   equal top speed available (no boost level)<br />\r\n   equal maneuverability<br />\r\n   identical hitbox<br />\r\n   no excuses<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHave no friends? That’s OK we built Vicky, an AI-powered bot that has nothing better to do than to play IMPULSE with you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWelcome to the beginning.<br />\r\nWelcome to IMPULSE.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n* controller only game because using a keyboard and mouse to play a game like this is weird.",
